We will help people who want to open a business or who have a new business, get credit cards and funding in their business name. Must have at least a 600+ credit score to qualify for this no money down option. Interested? Send me a DM with your business idea and credit score. #credit #businesscredit #entrepreneur #entrepreneurlife #creditscore #businesstips
